Author: James Gockel
Subject: Works
Body: For those with port issues: x runs on 6000 by default. Port forwarding from an SSH session should use 6000 and use the command ‘export DISPLAY=localhost:0‘ as 0 is the starting point for x displays @ port 6000. Export display is not to the said port number but to the x display number where 0 is port 6000.  Missing some render capabilities forces windows managers to fail, but seems like a good starting point for x on android!
